    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA326-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu tōḻi talaimakaṉai varaivu kaṭāyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how the confidante urged HIM for marriage.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA326">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            koḻuñcuḷaip palaviṉ payaṅkeḻu kavāaṟ</l>
<l>            ceḻuṅkōḷ vāṅkiya mācciṉaik kokkiṉ</l>
<l>            mīṉkuṭai nāṟṟan tāṅkal cellātu</l>
<l>            tuyttalai manti tummu nāṭa</l>
<l>            niṉakku muraitta ṉāṇuva livaṭkē</l>
<l>            nuṇkoṭip pīratti ṉūḻuṟu pūveṉap</l>
<l>            pacalai yūru maṉṉō paṉṉā</l>
<l>            ḷariyamar vaṉappiṉeṅ kāṉa naṇṇa</l>
<l>            vaṇṭeṉu muṇarā vāki</l>
<l>            malareṉa marīi varūumivaḷ kaṇṇē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O man from a land,</l>
<l rend="indent4">where the cotton-headed she-monkey sneezes,</l>
<l>since impossible to endure is the fragrance of the catch(?)<note place="foot">Actually <term xml:lang="ta">kuṭai</term> does not make any sense here, unless we are prepared to violate semantics. Should we emend to simply -<term xml:lang="ta">uṭai</term> - the fragrance of the fish?</note> of fish</l>
<l rend="indent">of the heron on the big branch, bent under the rich [fruit-] bunches</l>
<l rend="indent2">on the mountain slope with a yield of jack trees with rich pulp,</l>
<l rend="indent3">even of talking to you<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">niṉakkum uraittal</term>: here T.V.G. explains that -<term xml:lang="ta">um</term>, pragmatically belonging to <term xml:lang="ta">uraittal</term>, has changed position for metrical reasons.</note> on her behalf</l>
<l rend="indent4">I am ashamed.</l>
<l>Pallor, [recalling] the whithered flower of the Pīram in fine creepers,</l>
<l>is creeping up, alas, for many days</l>
<l rend="indent2">in her eyes, on which, taking [them] for blossoms, the bees</l>
<l rend="indent2">come joining together, being completely unaware,</l>
<l rend="indent3">when they come near our forest,</l>
<l rend="indent3">in [their] read-streaked desirable beauty.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
